Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州城 不愧为中原第一雄关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想当年楚霸王项羽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是在此地用三万铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀得高祖帝五十万兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是片甲不留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州让我魂牵梦绕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:03:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日终于美梦成真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一看便知 如此雄关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区吕布怎配据有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雄关 应当归属明主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日已成正果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公得徐州以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进可攻退可守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鼎立中原之日 为期不远也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说到吕布 我想起一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下如果没有猜错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公八成想起貂蝉来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布死了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉是不吃不喝 更不梳妆打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整天呆坐着 侍者问她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她只有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要为吕布收尸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要招惹貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此女太过妖艳 乱人心性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公休忘了董卓和吕布的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧啊 多谢你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我既非董卓 更非吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小姐 小姐请看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这些都是曹将军送你的服饰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}件件都是珍奇之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就连长安宫里的嫔妃们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小姐快快梳妆打扮起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹将军说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要小姐把这些衣服穿起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}侍候曹将军一次酒宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹将军什么条件都答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要为我夫君收尸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹将军准了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要楠木棺材一口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}六尺玉石一方 以王公之礼厚葬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}碑上还要锲明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汉都亭侯 奋威将军吕奉先之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹将军准了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我死后 要和我的夫君葬在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}准 都准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多亏各位将军奋勇拚杀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方能拿下徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我与各位将军同饮此杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一醉方休
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祝贺将军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来 满上满上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀先生 来来来 倒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们俩说什么都得喝好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 我真的喝不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别呀 等等 先生 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你叹什么气啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事 我真的没事 你喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你肯定有事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这大喜的日子你愁什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事 没事 真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 你肯定有事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要是不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就不让你走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许将军 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公喜欢女人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看你说的 谁不喜欢女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我许褚也喜欢女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和主公喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公喜欢的是已婚少妇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是别人家的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还记得张绣的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我当然记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公那天喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把降将张绣的小伯母召来侍寝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张绣不堪其辱 竟然乘夜攻杀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不是典韦护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公早死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}典将军就是为此丧的命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚主公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要比那天夜里更加危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么着 你快说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公已经发话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他今夜要去白门楼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道白门楼里住的是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个妖女怎么还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非但没死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还打扮得如花似玉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正准备接待主公哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚啊 你可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董卓和吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是因为貂蝉而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此女太过妖艳 乱人心肺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她一旦缠上主公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是祸水横流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定会殃及三军哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在就去除了祸水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎等等 你就不怕主公降罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我许褚跟随主公厮杀多年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}九死一生 何惧之有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}红牙催拍燕飞忙 一片行云到画堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眉黛促成游子恨 玉容初断故人肠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 如此长袖善舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知醉倒了多少英雄豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这一唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是为了将军 是为了我夫君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道在你心中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我曹操还比不上一个吕布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 在我心中将军是不如他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我夫君真诚 将军老辣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我夫君善良 将军奸险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我夫君多情 将军无义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以即便你是杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我心里你永远不如他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}七星刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你知道它的来历吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这你算是问对人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概在八百多年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一颗流星落在了越地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烧红了五十多里山川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当天夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干将 莫邪夫妇就取回了流星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}铸成了两把宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一把叫干将 一把叫莫邪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是吴王剑和越王剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}铸完这两把宝剑剩下的陨铁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能够锻造一把短刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这把七星刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}八百多年啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吴王剑和越王剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都已经是名满天下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是只有这把七星刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}默默无闻 一直不为人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我曹操执此刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刺杀董卓的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只可惜啊 董贼命不当绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天 你想用它来杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是要把它 还给上天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如今我就是天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妖妇 你休得放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她没想杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她只是想自杀 你这个匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她死得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是荀彧叫你来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己到监军那儿领三十军棍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罢了 免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不免 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大伙听着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此役 我们一举收取徐州六郡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}威震天下 实力大增
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也是咱们自起兵以来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}取得的最大的一场胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为此我足足高兴了半个时辰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是半个时辰之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的心情又倍觉沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为冀州袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讨伐公孙瓒的一战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正在激烈地进行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这几个月以来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍步步紧逼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公孙瓒是损兵折将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}照此下去用不了多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幽州就是袁绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此一来 这大汉天下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍一个人就独享了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}青 幽 并 冀四个州
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成为天下最大的诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们知道这意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}意味着 主公与袁绍之间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定有一场生死决战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此战 决定天下归属
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你们知道此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我最盼望什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公盼望的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在袁绍与公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最好不分胜败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拖得越久越好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以便让袁绍兵力受损
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为主公赢得时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为最后的决战做充分准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后天班师回许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整军备战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 为何发愁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操后天就要班师了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在想 我们该何去何从啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在徐州是他的掌中物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们无处容身了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操不是答应 让你做徐州牧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他还答应吕布做三军大元帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操不还我们徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我们屯驻小沛也成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥你为朝廷立下过汗马功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又为曹操受了这么多的委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道他连一座小城都不舍得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他若能准我驻小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我当然高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我根本就不想随他去许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在离这个人越远越好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翼德 你意如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我呀 我才不操那份闲心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥的意思那就是我的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟倒是省心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这老大个天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂能没咱容身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们愁个甚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}班师在即 其余的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都已经有所安排了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是有个人该如何处置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战前 你们仨 一个叫我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个叫我用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个叫我用后再杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在班师在即啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们该拿他怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布已亡 徐州已归属主公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备无处依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只好投奔主公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在杀他已经没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相反 用之更好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}物尽其利 人尽其才
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公也享受人间爱贤之美称
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问主公是否答应过刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令其做徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是有吧 我记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公明言吧 有还是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 主公不可食言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下建议 赐刘备为徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但只授其名份而不给其实权
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另派可靠将领驻守徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总揽军政民政
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备呢 令其驻守小沛即可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下附议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下也附议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有几位士绅父老求见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们听说主公要回许昌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大急 代表徐州五十万百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}向主公敬献万民书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 这真想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们刚到徐州没两天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州的百姓就如此爱戴咱们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}民心可依啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快请进来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小民卢义祖等 拜见曹大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜见曹大将军 快快请起 请起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等听说大将军就要返回许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特代表徐州六郡的百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}向大将军来敬呈万民书
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恳请大将军留下刘公玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他重新担任徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘公玄德 哦 即是刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.91,0:23:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真大将军 刘备爱民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦死后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备曾经担任过九个月的徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那九个月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我徐州最太平的时光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备与各乡镇定立约法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罢斥贪官 减轻赋税
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还建了三座便民桥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五百余丈河堤 引水灌溉农田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才有了五谷丰登 人丁兴旺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大将军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我徐州百姓直到现在还有口饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍然托福于刘备当初的德政
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等已多年未见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此贤明的主公了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恳请大将军留下刘备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:23:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恳请大将军留下刘备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备如此贤明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}堪当朝廷栋梁之才
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 让如此大才
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}担任区区一州的刺史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是太委屈他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样你们看好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.67,0:24:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我把你们这个万民书
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.77,0:24:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上呈朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.44,0:24:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把列位的心意表奏天子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.04,0:24:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让天子亲自敕封刘备 可好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.01,0:24:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢大将军 谢谢大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.69,0:24:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}决不能让这个刘备留守徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.00,0:24:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连小沛都不能让他驻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.50,0:25:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你刚才同意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.80,0:25:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让刘备在徐州挂个虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.14,0:25:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有名无实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你没有听到刚才那个士绅的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.08,0:25:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备在徐州已经深得民心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.88,0:25:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果让他挂个虚衔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.21,0:25:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}挂着挂着他就会变成实的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.42,0:25:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而咱们留在徐州的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.08,0:25:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就会变成虚的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.62,0:25:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个不得不防
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.39,0:25:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备不能留下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.96,0:25:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要把他带回许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.98,0:25:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.08,0:25:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子下诏了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.15,0:25:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他听说你是皇室后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.65,0:25:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又在徐州剿贼中立下大功
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.46,0:25:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}龙心大悦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.69,0:26:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣刘备 遥祝吾皇万安
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.67,0:26:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟 你想不想一睹天颜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.64,0:26:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下朝思暮想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.61,0:26:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那好 上车吧 随我去许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.21,0:26:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.98,0:26:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公 不是明天才班师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.15,0:26:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是三军将士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.78,0:26:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你我要先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.65,0:26:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说 旅途寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.59,0:26:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想和贤弟做个伴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.16,0:26:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下有几位兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你放心吧 我都安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.46,0:26:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日 曹仁会陪着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关 张 赵三位将军班师回京
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.74,0:26:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么贤弟 不想见天子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.68,0:26:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 在下遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.85,0:26:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.82,0:27:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇上有旨 宣百官入朝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.69,0:27:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇上有旨 宣百官入朝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.97,0:27:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吾皇万岁万岁万万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.18,0:27:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大将军曹操 奉旨觐见
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.69,0:27:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子赐我 入朝不拜 赞拜不名
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.80,0:27:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下明白
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.43,0:28:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣曹操拜见天子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.30,0:28:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿平身
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.33,0:28:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣奉旨进军徐州 擒杀贼将吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.10,0:28:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}收复徐州六郡十九城
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.51,0:28:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}俘敌十万 斩首两万
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.24,0:28:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另获战马兵器无数
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.92,0:28:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿立此殊勋 朕极为高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.29,0:28:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.95,0:28:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上承天威 下为黎民
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.46,0:28:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}中兴汉室 臣不敢居功
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.36,0:28:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿一举攻陷了寿春
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大败逆贼袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.93,0:28:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此次爱卿又人不卸甲 马不卸鞍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.07,0:28:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为朝廷收取了徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.64,0:29:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿已是名震四海 功垂天下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.31,0:29:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听旨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.51,0:29:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕拜爱卿为朝廷丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.28,0:29:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总领朝政
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.65,0:29:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加赠封地九千顷 民三万户
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.55,0:29:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣曹操 即谢天恩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.40,0:29:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请曹丞相入座
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.97,0:29:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下请
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.49,0:29:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 你看这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.09,0:29:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他叫刘备 字玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.43,0:30:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘爱卿 请上殿来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.68,0:30:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣刘备叩见陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.32,0:30:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿祖上何方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.19,0:30:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣乃中山靖王之后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.96,0:30:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孝景皇帝之玄孙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.39,0:30:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祖刘雄之孙 父刘弘之子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.46,0:30:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是朕的皇亲哪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.40,0:30:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快拿皇族世谱来 朕要验看
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.58,0:30:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}念与朕听
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.28,0:30:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孝景皇帝生子十四
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.79,0:30:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第七子便是中山靖王刘胜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.35,0:30:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘胜生陆城侯刘贞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.46,0:31:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘贞生沛侯刘昂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.46,0:31:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘昂生漳侯刘禄
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.39,0:31:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘禄生沂侯刘恋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.36,0:31:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘恋生阳侯刘英
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.40,0:31:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘达生丰灵侯刘不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.90,0:31:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘不疑生济川侯刘惠
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘惠生东郡令刘雄
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.10,0:31:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘雄生刘弘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.61,0:31:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘弘不仕 生刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.71,0:31:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.81,0:31:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这刘备乃是孝景皇帝的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.85,0:31:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第十八代玄孙也
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.45,0:31:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依族谱 你是朕的皇叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.82,0:31:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下天恩浩荡 刘备感激涕零
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连年兵祸 使得国家蒙难
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.23,0:31:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕也饱受乱贼欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.34,0:31:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幸得曹丞相忠君报国 除贼安民
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.25,0:31:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迁都于许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.91,0:31:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕才略享偏安之福
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.42,0:32:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日见了刘皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.22,0:32:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕更是欢喜不尽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.52,0:32:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备听旨
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.29,0:32:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕授你为左将军 宜城亭侯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.93,0:32:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣 叩谢天恩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.90,0:32:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿闲暇时
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.27,0:32:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请多多进宫来看望朕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.37,0:32:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕想跟你述祖
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.40,0:32:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.31,0:32:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜刘皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.33,0:32:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜刘皇叔拜将封侯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.41,0:32:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜刘皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.22,0:33:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相虽然位极人臣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.62,0:33:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但还仍然是臣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.59,0:33:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而他刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.52,0:33:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转眼间便成了皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.59,0:33:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可笑之至啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.33,0:33:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.26,0:33:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要是愿意做他皇爷爷都成
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.56,0:33:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又不贪那个
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.97,0:33:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这陛下刚见刘备 就给他拜将封侯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.57,0:33:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很明显 陛下是想培植势力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.21,0:33:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用于外援 丞相不得不防啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.95,0:33:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此一节 我也想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.32,0:33:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然要防 不过凡事皆有利弊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.05,0:33:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备现在既然贵为皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.66,0:33:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以后我再用天子诏令制约他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.33,0:33:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他就更得遵从了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.10,0:33:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 极是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.23,0:33:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘皇叔受封后
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.00,0:33:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有没有得意忘形啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.07,0:33:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恰恰相反
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.00,0:34:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他受封之后 反而更加谦卑了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.01,0:34:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他把自己关在客宅里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.98,0:34:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整天是大门不出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.55,0:34:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即便是出门拜客
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.75,0:34:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大老远就打躬做揖 如履薄冰
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.16,0:34:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聪明人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.66,0:34:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 在下有一言 压抑很久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.23,0:34:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你只管说
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.43,0:34:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相无论在朝在野
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.54,0:34:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都已经是功德浩荡 恩威齐天了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.77,0:34:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.94,0:34:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相不应该仅仅屈尊于
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.48,0:34:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相之位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.75,0:34:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程昱 你是在劝进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.35,0:34:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.79,0:34:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.33,0:34:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在虽然功名日盛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.49,0:34:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是资望尚浅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.26,0:35:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵马属地也不如袁绍多
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.13,0:35:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.63,0:35:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在朝廷内外忠于天子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.70,0:35:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一心扶汉的大臣不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.41,0:35:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别人不说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.48,0:35:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧头一个他就不能答应
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.38,0:35:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我还是别惹火烧身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.78,0:35:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那丞相 你应该早做谋划
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.45,0:35:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}察清谁是帝党
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.56,0:35:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁忠诚于丞相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.00,0:35:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这倒可以
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.27,0:35:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.47,0:35:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过两天我要去许田行猎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.64,0:35:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}劳你进宫奏报天子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.24,0:35:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说我请他一块儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.85,0:35:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.05,0:35:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷内外的文武大臣都去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.92,0:35:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.50,0:36:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祖上如此辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.87,0:36:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惜传到朕这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.83,0:36:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却是奸贼当道 国家沦丧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.64,0:36:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惜哉 痛哉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.58,0:36:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.02,0:36:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚诏见刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.16,0:36:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何就给他拜将封侯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.23,0:36:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操独擅朝政
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.47,0:36:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}国事都不由朕做主
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.94,0:36:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备既是个英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.54,0:36:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是皇族后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.51,0:36:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太难得了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将来此人可用作后援哪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.51,0:36:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.72,0:37:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可刘备兵马不多
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.85,0:37:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又无甚属地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.52,0:37:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.33,0:37:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕将来会慢慢地封赏他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.20,0:37:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陛下 参军程昱求见
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.71,0:37:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 叫进来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.34,0:37:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.59,0:37:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣程昱拜见陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.46,0:37:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平身
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.93,0:37:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.73,0:37:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿有何事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.66,0:37:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真陛下 后天
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.23,0:37:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相请陛下许田行猎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.20,0:37:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿啊 这架鹰牵狗的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.14,0:37:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕不是天子正道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.14,0:38:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再者 朕的身体也不舒服 朕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.98,0:38:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 自古以来 圣君都好打猎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.18,0:38:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}春播夏种 秋收冬藏
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.55,0:38:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四时狩猎 扬威于天下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.12,0:38:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹丞相不但请陛下出猎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.46,0:38:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还令朝廷大臣 三军将士随驾
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.73,0:38:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们都盼望着跟随陛下行猎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.17,0:38:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}至于陛下所说的龙体欠安嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.07,0:38:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣 敢请陛下三思
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.81,0:38:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听爱卿说话的这会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.88,0:38:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕的身体舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.35,0:38:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转告丞相 朕去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.39,0:38:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}领旨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.13,0:39:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣替陛下试射一箭
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.14,0:39:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.54,0:39:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.71,0:39:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万岁 万岁 万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.63,0:40:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相神射 真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.97,0:40:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这恐怕不是刘皇叔的心里话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.84,0:40:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可是见过吕布的辕门射戟的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.18,0:40:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他才堪称神射二字
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布虽然善射 却被丞相斩首了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.05,0:40:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相箭术虽不如吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.59,0:40:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却能一箭定江山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.56,0:40:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此看来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.19,0:40:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布射技再高也是俗射
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.60,0:40:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而丞相虽只射翻一头鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.27,0:40:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}堪当是神射
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.00,0:40:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这倒是句实话 中听
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.64,0:40:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣奉还陛下的宝雕弓
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.38,0:40:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿留着用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.38,0:40:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢陛下赐弓
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.32,0:40:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万岁 万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.36,0:41:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚 在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.87,0:41:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送你了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 这弓软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.04,0:41:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么用 要它干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.50,0:41:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就把它扔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.31,0:41:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程昱 在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.44,0:41:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才的事你都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.51,0:41:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将士们向我高呼万岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.48,0:41:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有多少人不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.95,0:41:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}国舅董承气得满脸通红
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.45,0:41:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽已伸手摸剑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.22,0:41:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不少大臣也是敢怒不敢言
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.22,0:41:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有荀彧 他也长吁短叹
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.42,0:41:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.26,0:41:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我对他那么信任那么敬重
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.66,0:41:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他却心向天子
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.70,0:41:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.16,0:41:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由此可见
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.87,0:41:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷上下忠于陛下的人不在少数
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.40,0:41:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更何况现在 诸侯割据 枭雄争霸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.84,0:41:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}称帝的事 就不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.14,0:41:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.75,0:41:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 许田打围
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.99,0:42:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操实在太可恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.52,0:42:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢压皇帝一头
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.29,0:42:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抢夺天子之礼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.53,0:42:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操帝王之志 僭位之心
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.53,0:42:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早就有目共睹了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.27,0:42:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我本来想杀了曹贼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.90,0:42:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为国除害
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.50,0:42:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可大哥你为什么不许我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.28,0:42:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当时曹操身边甲士林立
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.78,0:42:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}猛将如云 如果你动手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.48,0:42:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我担心不但伤不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.92,0:42:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而会害了天子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.79,0:42:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在不除曹贼 日后必成大患
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.33,0:42:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.50,0:42:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这杀又杀不得 忍又忍不得
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.70,0:42:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那咱们还窝在这里干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.97,0:42:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥咱不如离开许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.14,0:42:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到外头快活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.44,0:43:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在许昌各处都把守极严
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.21,0:43:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们即使想走
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.81,0:43:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也要寻找机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.28,0:43:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们现在寄人篱下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.75,0:43:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万事都要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.19,0:43:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 你老是忍耐忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.99,0:43:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这忍到何时是个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.83,0:43:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘘 低声
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.57,0:43:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 皇宫里来了个内臣
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.43,0:43:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说是传天子口谕
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.11,0:43:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣刘备听旨
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.32,0:43:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀刘皇叔 圣上口谕
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.35,0:43:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下在许田行猎时
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.99,0:43:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身染寒露 卧病不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.22,0:43:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诏各位皇亲国戚入宫请安
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.50,0:43:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请奏报陛下 臣立刻就去
